code: const pick=(obj,...keys)=>keys.flat().filter(key=>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(obj,key)).reduce((acc,key)=>{acc[key]=obj[key];return acc;},{});const omit=(obj,...keysToOmit)=>{const keysToOmitSet=new Set(keysToOmit.flat());return Object.getOwnPropertyNames(obj).filter(key=>!keysToOmitSet.has(key)).reduce((acc,key)=>{acc[key]=obj[key];return acc;},{});};module.exports={pick,omit};
